	<texsetting wysiwyg="0"/><paper pagenumber="1" margin="20,20,20,25">A4</paper></head><body fontsize="12pt" fontface="ＭＳ Ｐ明朝">
<p>この積分で<mblock><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit></mblock>は円<mblock><munit entity="1">Gamma</munit></mblock>の上にあるから<mblock><munit>|</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">z</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">a</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">a</munit></mlink></munit><munit>|</munit><munit>&lt;</munit><munit>1</munit></mblock>である。従って、</p>
<p><mblock><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">z</munit></mlink></munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>(</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">a</munit><munit>)</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">z</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">a</munit><munit>)</munit></mlink></munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">a</munit></mlink></munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit>1</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">z</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">a</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">a</munit></mlink></munit></melem><mlink type="rsup"><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit>1</munit></mlink></marray><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">a</munit></mlink></munit><marray type="curly"><melem><munit>1</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">z</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">a</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">a</munit></mlink></munit><munit>+</munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">z</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">a</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">a</munit></mlink></munit></melem><mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></marray><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit>+</munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">z</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">a</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">a</munit></mlink></munit></melem><mlink type="rsup"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></marray><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit></melem></marray></mblock></p>
<p>これを(1)の右辺に代入すれば、</p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">z</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>=</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">pi</munit><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1" style="big">int<mlink type="rsub"><munit entity="1">Gamma</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit><munit>)</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">a</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">d</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit><munit>+</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">z</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">a</munit><munit>)</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">pi</munit><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1" style="big">int<mlink type="rsub"><munit entity="1">Gamma</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit><munit>)</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>(</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">a</munit><munit>)<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">d</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit>+</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">z</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">a</munit><munit>)<mlink type="rsup"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">pi</munit><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1" style="big">int<mlink type="rsub"><munit entity="1">Gamma</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit><munit>)</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>(</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">a</munit><munit>)<mlink type="rsup"><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit>+</munit><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">d</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit></mblock>   (2)</p>
<p>ここで積分表示を利用すれば、</p>
<p><mblock><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">pi</munit><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1" style="big">int<mlink type="rsub"><munit entity="1">Gamma</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit><munit>)</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">a</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">d</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">a</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>,</munit><munit> </munit><munit> </munit><munit> </munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">pi</munit><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1" style="big">int<mlink type="rsub"><munit entity="1">Gamma</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit><munit>)</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>(</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">a</munit><munit>)<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">d</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">f<mlink type="rsup"><munit entity="1">prime</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">a</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>,</munit><munit> </munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit>,</munit></mblock></p>
<p><mblock><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit>!</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">pi</munit><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1" style="big">int<mlink type="rsub"><munit entity="1">Gamma</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit><munit>)</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>(</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">a</munit><munit>)<mlink type="rsup"><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit>+</munit><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">d</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">zeta</munit><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">f<mlink type="rsup"><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit>)</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">a</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>,</munit><munit> </munit><munit> </munit><munit> </munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit></mblock></p>
<p>これらを(2)に代入すれば、式が成立する。</p>
<p/>
<p>この定理で<mblock><munit italic="1">a</munit><munit>=</munit><munit>0</munit></mblock>である場合に、<mblock><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">z</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>の展開は、</p>
<p><mblock><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">z</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit>0</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">f<mlink type="rsup"><munit entity="1">prime</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit>0</munit><munit>)</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>1</munit><munit>!</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">z</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">f<mlink type="rsup"><munit entity="1">prime</munit><munit entity="1">prime</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit>0</munit><munit>)</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit>2</munit><munit>!</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">z<mlink type="rsup"><munit>2</munit></mlink></munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">f<mlink type="rsup"><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit>)</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit>0</munit><munit>)</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit>!</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">z<mlink type="rsup"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit></mblock></p>
<p>となる。これを関数<mblock><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">z</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>のマクローリン展開という。</p>
